\is1 Introduction
\ip \bk The first sulat ni Pidru\bk*, insulat din para te migmalintutuu nekegsuwey-suwey nangugpe diye dapit te Asya Minur. The tuyu ni Pidru te migsulat kayi, ka pegbagget te migmalintutuu keilangan eglig‑en sikandan taliware te masumpit pegbayad-bayad kandan tenged te pegpalintutuu ran. Impasuman-suman sikandan ni Pidru meyitenged te kaluwasan dan, te kamatayen ni Hisu Kristu, te pegkeuyag din and te peglibed din. Su nanengnengan ni Pidru emun ke iyan dan layun egsumsumanen ka egpallatengen dan diye te langit, egkaantus dan iya ka langun keyirapan kayi te ampew te tane. Impanengneng din man‑e sikandan emun ke egkeehet ka pegpalintutuu ran pinaahi te peg-antus dan te me keyirapan and me kalasayan, egpakarawat sikandan te dasag te “Timpu igpakite e si Hisu Kristu.” (1:7,13)
\ip Migbanasalan din man‑e sikandan keilangan eg-ay-ayaran dan ka batasan dan isip me keet-etawan ni Kristu, and keilangan degma egparuma-ruma sikandan te seeye se due katenged egmandu kandan.
\iot Main components of this “book”
\io1 Introduction \ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 The pegpasuman-suman meyitenged te kaluwasan ware katamanan \ior 1:3-12\ior*
\io1 The pegbanasal meyitenged te peg-ugpe matulus \ior 1:13–2:10\ior*
\io1 The pegparuma-ruma ta te seeye se due me katenged diye te kanta \ior 2:11–3:7\ior*
\io1 The tambag meyitenged te egginguma me keyirapan \ior 3:8–4:19\ior*
\io1 The tambag para te pangulu and te migmalintutuu \ior 5:1-11\ior*
\io1 The me pangemusta \ior 5:12-14\ior*
